Experience the warm hospitality of The Studio Guest House, where a delicious English breakfast and seasonal outdoor pool set the tone for a relaxing stay. With free in-room WiFi, conference center, and access to nearby health club facilities - along with convenient perks like luggage storage and barbecue grills - guests can unwind in style.
